item.title: The Einstein Show - June 28, 2013
item.description: Hour 1 - Phone Calls, plus some 'Show and Tell' photos from the einsteinshow.net website, and Kidsville, USA slips in right before the end of the hour. Hour 2 - More with Kidsville, USA plus the Texas Belles, Donna, Kristine, and Ann Marie stop by for a visit. (See also Kristine & Friends Naked Around Town) Hour 3 - More with the Texas Belles plus a really big announcement from Einstein producer Mikey D.
